title: S12 Ep63: The 27 Club & The Death of Paul McCartney?
itunes:title: The 27 Club & The Death of Paul McCartney?
description:
We dig into the Darkives and look at the frightening number of musicians that belong to The 27 Club, a grouping of musical powerhouses that never lived past the age of 27 and examine the strange death hoax surrounding Paul McCartney with author, R. Gary Patterson.

R. Gary Patterson: http://www.rgarypatterson.com/
